title: Ebro In the Morning - Rosenberg and Wiz Squash their Beef + Ebro Reflects on George Floyd
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning.

In this episode, Ebro reflects on the death of George Floyd (30:00) and the crew discusses parenting (50:00), Wiz Khalifa & Rosenberg bury the hatchet (20:20), and Kyrie Irving (1:13:00).
